      section.index-how.center
        .container
          h2 How Can We Help?
          .flex.flex-wrap
            .flex-1
              img(src="assets/img/consulting.png", alt="consulting")
              h3 Consulting
              p Is your organisation finding it difficult to navigate through the current uncertain times? We work with enterprises helping them navigate and come out a winner through these VUCA times.
            .flex-1
              img(src="assets/img/software-dev.png", alt="software development")
              h3 Software Development
              p Software is changing how businesses are run at every level. We can help build the software that’s right for your requirements.
            .flex-1
              img(src="assets/img/training.png", alt="training")
              h3 Training
              p Training on various software practices for the complete workforce. Right from the junior developers on how to use GIT well to experienced software architects on Object-Oriented Programming and DevOps.

