              img(src="assets/img/jayram-joshi.png", alt="jayram joshi")
              h3 Jayram Joshi
              h4 CEO
              p With over 20 years of work experience, Jayram has worked with some of the leading brands in varying roles across domains. His journey started as a project manager and evolved to roles like that of Cheif Technical Officer, Head of Product Development who grew to become a Leadership Coach, Mentor and now the Founder. A Technologist and Entrepreneur at heart, Jayram is always curious to learn and grow.
            .flex-1
              img(src="assets/img/shripad-agashe.png", alt="shripad agashe")
              h3 Shripad Agashe
              h4 CTO
              p With over 17 years of development experience in building enterprise-scale software, Shripad is an expert in TDD with a special interest in Performance and Scalability of compute-intensive enterprise applications. “Been there, done that.” is the perfect phrase to define Shripad’s technical expertise which has evolved from a System Engineer to a Senior Technical Architect. Even though the sceptical one in the team, Shripad too is ever-curious about the latest the tech market has to offer.

